Package: EnsDb.Osativa.IRGSP.62
Title: Ensembl-Based Annotation for Oryza sativa IRGSP-1.0 (Release 62)
Description: Provides the Ensembl Plants gene, transcript, and exon
    annotations for the rice genome assembly IRGSP-1.0, based on the
    official Ensembl release 62. Gene IDs follow the RAP-DB nomenclature
    (OsXXgXXXXXXX) and are complemented with MSU v7.0 functional
    descriptions where available.
Version: 0.99.0
